Package menuPackage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MenuFunctions
    This class has all the functionalities of the menu.
    MenuManager
    This class is the user interface between the program and the user.
    MenuPrint
    Menu class which means that the main functionality of this class is to show to the user the input that has to enter to make certain functions.
    RandomPeopleGenerator
    This class is a singleton and generates random Person objects from a sample of names, surnames, genders, cities and movies list.
